{{Item|sellValue={{Money|0.23|size=8}}|research=Ground Water Pump|itemImage=Icon-water.png|resValue={{RP|0x }}}}
==Information==
'''Water''' is a versatile liquid harvested by the [[Water Pump]] as well as its upgraded sister, the [[Water Pump2]]. It is an invaluable ingredient for a myriad of machines across all stages of the game.

Future updates may provide more methods of obtaining '''Water''', as the [[Water Pump]] and [[Water Pump2]] are currently the only viable methods of producing said liquid. While the [[Condenser]], a {{Tier||3}} machine involved in the production of [[Water-Free Gas]], can produce '''Water''', its yield is negligible.

==Usage==
'''Water''' is extremely special in that it has an exceptionally wide variety of uses, a variety that no other materials in the game can even compare to. '''Water''' can be used in the following:

*It is a required fluid for the {{Tier||1}} [[Coal Generator]] to function.
*It can be utilized in a [[Large Turbine]] setup, as it is the only fluid that a [[Boiler]] can convert to [[Steam]].
*It can be used in a [[Tree Farm]] setup to irrigate the [[Tree|Trees]].
*It can be filtered in a [[Filtration Plant]] to be used for a number of purposes.
*It is a required ingredient of [[Ethanol]].
*It can be bottled in a [[Bottling Plant]], though it is outclassed by [[Filtered Water]] or [[Refined Diesel|Refined Diesel]].
*It is required to run [[Soil Excavator|Soil Excavators]], [[Trommel|Trommels]] and [[Pressurized Water Filter|Pressurized Water Filters]] in the production of [[Gold]].
*It can be input in a [[Scrubber]] to remove {{Pollution|3.24}}/hr.
*It can be input into an [[Electrolysis Plant]] to receive [[Hydrogen]] and [[Oxygen]].
*It can be input in a [[Mineshaft Drill]] to decrease the amount of the durability usage, though this is far outclassed by any acid.
*It can be distilled in a [[Water Treatment Plant]] or [[Atmospheric Distillation Plant]].
*It is needed for the [[Foundry]] to mold ingots.

