==Trivia==
<ul><li>'''Water''' is the single item/fluid with the most usage in the entire game, being included in an astounding 6 recipes.</li>
<li>'''Water''' is the only fluid that does not produce [[Pollution]] when destroyed in a [[Liquid Dump]]/[[Liquid Burner|Liquid Burner.]] This property does not extend to its variants, [[Filtered Water]] and [[Distilled Water]].</li></ul>

