{{Item|title1=Crude Oil|research=Oil Extraction|sellValue={{money|11.6|size=8}}|itemImage=Icon-crude-oil.png|resValue={{RP|0.2x }}}}
==Information==
'''Crude Oil''' is a versatile liquid extracted directly using an [[Oil Rig]] or a [[Large Pumpjack]], produced as a by-product of converting [[Raw Gas]] into [[Water-Free Gas]] in a [[Condenser]], distilled from [[Fracking Oil]] in an [[Atmospheric Distillation Plant]], generated as a by-product of processing [[Light Oil]] or [[Fracking Oil]] through an [[Industrial Oil Separator]], or derived from filtering [[Heavy Oil]] through a [[Filtration Plant]]. 

This essential product serves as a foundation for producing [[oil]]-based products. 

==Usage==
*Heating it up using a [[Liquid Boiler]], then using a [[Crude Oil Separator]] to convert into [[Crude Diesel]], [[Gasoline]] and [[Residue]].
*Using in a [[Steam Cracking Plant]] to produce [[Paraxylene]] and [[Ethylene]] (mainly used for [[Plastic]] production)
*Inputting into a [[Coal Liquefaction Plant]] along with [[Coal]] and [[Steam]] to produce [[Light Oil]], [[Heavy Oil]] and [[Residue]].
*Inputting into a [[Plastic Refinery]] along with [[Water]] to produce [[Ethanol]].

