==Trivia==
*[[Hot Crude Oil]] and '''Crude Oil''' are two separate fluids that cannot be used interchangeably. [[Hot Crude Oil]] is what is used in a [[Crude Oil Separator]] but it can be used also for [[Boiler|Boilers]].
*'''Crude Oil''' is the darkest liquid in the game.
*'''Crude Oil''' is the most useful liquid in the game after [[Water]].
*There are five different types of '''Oil''' in the game.
*As of {{Update|0.11.3}}, the best way to get this resource in bulk is by putting [[Fracking Oil]] into [[Industrial Oil Separator]].

