{{Top-bottle}}{{Item|itemImage=Icon-refined-diesel-bottle.png|sellValue={{Money|449.5|size=8}}|research=Water Bottling|resValue={{RP|15x }}}} ==Information== The '''Refined Diesel Bottle''' is an item made by putting [[Refined Diesel]] into a [[Bottling Plant]] along with [[Bottle|Plastic Bottles]].
Producing '''Refined Diesel Bottles''' is highly discouraged, as the value of [[Refined Diesel]] will only increase by around 16%<ref>Not including the [[Plastic Bottle|plastic bottle]]</ref>, and considering the complexity of plastic, the diesel can be better used as fuel for a [[Modular Diesel Engine]].
