==Trivia==
*'''Acetic Acid''' is the first acid to be added to the game.
*'''Acetic Acid''' is the weakest acid currently in the game, behind the [[Hydrochloric Acid]] and [[Sulfuric Acid]].
**This is also the simplest acid to make, requiring only four different machines and two optional.
