{{Item|itemImage=Icon-sand.png|research=Sand excavator|sellValue={{Money|5}}|resValue={{RP|0.1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Sand''' is obtained by feeding [[Soil]] and [[Water]] into a [[Trommel]] or  formerly excavated by a [[Sand Excavator]].  Now mainly obtained through a ''[[Quarry]],'' '''Sand''' is an essential precursor for [[Microchip|Microchips]] in the form of [[Silicon]] or as the main material for making [[Glass]]. It is also a required input in the [[Oil Fracking Tower]], generating excessive amounts of '''Sand''' is not typically necessary for the [[Oil Fracking Tower]] as it only requires one [[Sand Excavator]].  

== Usage ==
'''Sand''' is used for [[Silicon]] production for [[Microchip|Microchips]], as well being required for [[Oil Fracking Tower|Oil Fracking]] to create large scale [[Diesel Refinery|diesel production]] for huge [[Modular Diesel Engine]]/[[Large Diesel Engine]] setups, though the former is better. '''Sand''' is also used for creating [[Filter|Filters]] to be used inside an [[Exhaust Stack]] reducing its emissions, playing a key part in [[Coal Power Plant]] setups.

