==Trivia== 
*'''Sand''' is essentially the result of erosion in [[Rock|Rocks]]. This process can be replicated by scraping a wet rock against another at a beach, it will turn to '''Sand''' over an insane amount of time. This reflects the erosion process, though said erosion occurs over thousands of years when [[Water]] grinds down [[Rock|Rocks]]. '''Sand''' is also a very important component in [[Soil]], allowing the compound to be fertile and adequate for plant growth. Since '''Sand''' is basically [[Rock|Rocks]], it also contains trace amounts of minerals, which are also filtered out in the in-game [[Trommel]].
