==Trivia==
* '''Machine Oil''' could be used in the [[Presents Packing Machine]] during the [[Christmas Event 2023|2023 Christmas Event]] to speed up its production by eight times regular speed. The [[Presents Packing Machine]] is no longer available and thus '''Machine Oil''' cannot be used for this purpose.

