{{Item|itemImage=icon-gold-ingot.png|sellValue={{Money|4,250}}|research=Industrial electric furnace|resValue={{RP|70x }}}}
==Information==
'''Gold Ingots''' can be created by smelting [[Gold]] through an [[Industrial Electric Furnace]] to get [[Liquid Gold]] which can be put through an [[Ingot Molder]] to output '''Gold Ingots'''.

The higher the karat of the [[Gold]] smelted, the more [[Liquid Gold]] will be outputted.

