{{Item|itemImage=icon-gravel.png|research=Trommel|sellValue={{Money|4}}|resValue={{RP|0.1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Gravel''' is created by inputting [[Soil]] into a [[Trommel]] or [[Grinder]], with the latter having a higher yield than the former. It is typically found as a byproduct of [[Gold]] production.

==Usage==
If '''Gravel''' is obtained as an unwanted byproduct of [[Gold]] production, it is best to convert it into [[Sand]], and then process it into [[Glass]] or [[Silicon]]. Extracting '''Gravel''' directly from Soil for the purpose of obtaining [[Sand]] is highly discouraged, as using a [[Sand Excavator]] both yields more [[Sand]] and consumes less Power. '''Gravel''' can also be used to double the efficiency of [[Filter]] production chains.
[[Category:Items]]

