{{Item|itemImage=Icon-alumina-dust.png|research=Trommel|sellValue={{Money|90}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Alumina Dust''' is an item created by shredding [[Alumina]] in a [[Grinder]], yielding '''Alumina Dust'''. It can then be melted in an [[Industrial Electric Furnace]] to produce [[Liquid Aluminium]]. 

==Usage==
As of {{Update|0.11.3}}, '''Alumina Dust''' only functions as a bridge between [[Alumina]] and [[Liquid Aluminium]], having a low sale value compared to its succeeding compounds. As such, it is encouraged to melt and mold it into [[Aluminium Ingot|Aluminium Ingots]], only leaving it to be sold when the [[Money]] required to purchase an [[Industrial Electric Furnace]] is unavailable. 

