{{Item|title1=Molten Purple Gold|itemImage=Icon-molten-purple-gold.png|research=Alloyer|sellValue={{Money|580}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}} ==Information== '''Molten Purple Gold''' is used to make [[Purple Gold Ingot]] with an [[Ingot Molder]]. It can be produced by combining a [[Gold Ingot]] and two [[Aluminium Ingot|Aluminum Ingots]] in an [[Alloyer]] with [[Steam]]. Unlocked after [[Alloyer]]
== Usage == Selling '''Molten Purple Gold''' is highly discouraged, as [[Purple Gold Ingot]] are extremely easy to produce and yield a much higher profit than their liquid predecessor. It is only used as a stepping stone from [[Gold Ingot]] and [[Aluminium Ingot]] to [[Purple Gold Ingot]].
