{{Item|research=Industrial Furnace|sellValue={{Money|80}}|itemImage=icon-glass.png|resValue={{RP|14x }}}} ==Information== '''Glass''' is an item made by inputting [[Liquid Glass]] into [[Ingot Molder]]. '''Glass''' production is a side product of the [[Gold]] industry, coming from the separated [[Sand]] and [[Gravel]] which is then crushed and smelted into '''Glass'''.
One unit of '''Glass''' requires two liters of [[Liquid Glass]], roughly translating to four units of [[Sand]]. '''Glass''' cannot be shaped or formed into further products.
==Usage== As of {{Update|0.11.3}}, '''Glass''' is only useful for selling purposes. A byproduct of [[Gold]] and [[Aluminium Ingot|Aluminium]] production, '''Glass''' is generally regarded as a method of disposing the excess [[Sand]] and [[Gravel]] formed by the usage of a [[Trommel]]. It directly competes with [[Silicon]] for this purpose, as both items can be made from excess [[Sand]]. Although more [[Money]] can be generated by producing the aforementioned, '''Glass''' is valued for its simplistic production line and greater sale value per unit.
Due to the involvement of an [[Industrial Electric Furnace]] in the '''Glass''' production chain, melting residual [[Sand]] formed by [[Purple Gold Ingot|Purple Gold]] factories into '''Glass''' is discouraged due to the stated machine's expensive price. However, machine chains forming [[Gold Wire]] for the [[Logic Assembler]] should have their leftover [[Sand]] melted into '''Glass''', as the [[Industrial Electric Furnace|Industrial Electric Furnace's]] price swiftly becomes irrelevant in such later phases of the game.
==Recipes== {{Production|input1=liquid-glass|Input1Amount=4|time=4|Mamyflux=150MF|output1=glass|Output1Amount=2|machine=Ingot Molder}}
==Trivia== *'''Glass''' is an amorphous solid, meaning that its contained molecules are suspended in a disorderly pattern instead of a uniform crystal lattice. [[Category:Items]] {{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|itemImage=Icon-iron-powder.png|research=Utility|sellValue={{Money|15}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Iron Powder''' is produced by inputting [[Raw Iron]] into a [[Grinder]]. It's a necessary ingredient in the production of [[Iron Mix]], which can then be converted to [[Steel]] in a [[Blast Furnace]] or turned into large amounts of [[Liquid Iron]] in an [[Advanced Electric Furnace|(Advanced)]] [[Electric Furnace]].

== Usage ==
'''Iron Powder''' has only one main use, besides selling, which is being turned into [[Iron Mix]].  

'''Iron Powder''' is also used to double the output of [[Clay Brick]] in the [[Concrete Plant]].  

[[Iron Mix]] has a higher Unit to [[Liquid Iron]] Ratio than [[Raw Iron]], being the main reason why it is produced, however it is not recommended for late game players as [[Treated Raw Iron]] has an even higher [[Liquid Iron]] yield.

