{{Item|itemImage=Icon-copper-mix.png|research=Steel|sellValue={{Money|3}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Copper Mix''' is produced by inputting [[Coke Fuel]] or [[Coal]] and [[Copper Powder]] into a [[Blast Furnace]] or an [[Industrial Kiln]]. As of {{Update|0.11.3}}, the only use for '''Copper Mix''' is producing [[Liquid Copper]] in the [[Advanced Electric Furnace|(Advanced)]] [[Electric Furnace]]. It is not recommended to produce '''Copper Mix''' for money as by the time players unlock the [[Blast Furnace]], they would have moved on from [[Copper]] as a [[Money Making]] method.

== Usage ==
'''Copper mix''' can be used in farms that have a high volume [[Copper Ingot]] requirement. The main farms that require lots of [[Copper Ingot|Copper Ingots]] include [[Microchip]] production and [[Insulated Wire]] production (used for making [[Electromagnet|Electromagnets]], and even further [[Electric Motor|Electric Motors]]). While creating '''Copper Mix''' is not necessary, it can be used to minimise space used up while creating a factory. 

