{{Item|itemImage=Icon-liquid-glass.png|research=Industrial Electric Furnace|sellValue={{Money|10}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Liquid Glass''' can be obtained by inputting [[Sand]] into [[Industrial Electric Furnace]] and is necessary to produce [[Glass]] with the use of the [[Ingot Molder]].

== Usage ==
'''Liquid Glass''' has no practical use, as making [[Glass]] is not worth it for the financial gains, and turning sand into '''Liquid Glass''' is not worth it, as it can be used in [[Oil Fracking Tower|Oil Fracking Towers]], but if the [[Sand]] is a byproduct then selling [[Glass]] for extra money is worth it, as it takes practically nothing to make.

