{{Item|title1=Iron Plate<sup>2</sup>|research=Iron Press|sellValue={{Money|295.8}}|itemImage=Icon-iron-plate^2.png|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
The '''Iron Plate<sup>2</sup>''' is an [[Items|Item]] with no secondary uses beyond selling. It is produced by processing an [[Iron Plate]] inside a [[Press]] or inside the [[Press MK2]].

When using a [[Press]] the '''Iron Plate<sup>2</sup>''' is comparable to [[Iron Coil|Iron Coils]] in terms of production efficiency. Although '''Iron Plate<sup>2</sup>''' sells for a higher price, it requires four [[Iron Plate|Iron Plates]] to produce one unit. In contrast, four [[Iron Plate|Iron Plates]] can also be used to create eight [[Iron Coil|Iron Coils]], therefore making '''Iron PlateÂ²''' production not recommended as 8 [[Iron Coil|Iron Coils]] sells for a total of {{Money|350.8}} meaning that {{Money|55}} is lost when selling one '''Iron PlateÂ²'''.

However, this dynamic shifts significantly when using a [[Press MK2|Press Mk2]]. When using the [[Press MK2]]'s secret recipe combined with the [[Industrial Sawmill]]'s [[Iron Plate]] recipe, allows an '''Iron Plate<sup>2</sup>''' to compete with [[Gearbox|Gearboxes]] in terms of profitability. While a [[Gearbox]] setup is slightly cheaper in terms of both [[Money]] and [[RP]], an '''Iron Plate<sup>2</sup>''' farm requires less [[MamyFlux|Power]] and is easier to construct.

