==High/Low pressure Steam==
[[High Pressure Steam]] can be created by using [[Heat Exchanger]] instead of normal [[Boiler]], [[High Pressure Steam]] goes in [[Modular Turbine|Modular Turbine's]] Turbine input then [[High Pressure Turbine]], [[Intermediate Pressure Turbine]], [[Low Pressure Turbine]], Generator and Turbine Output which will output the [[Low Pressure Steam]] which can be used in [[Steam Condenser|Condenser]] to convert into [[Distilled Water]].
[[Category:Fluids]]
{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|research=Gas Condenser/Oil Fracking|sellValue={{Money|0.14}}|itemImage=Icon-water-free-gas.png|resValue={{RP|0x }}}}
==Information==
'''Water-Free Gas''' is produced when [[Raw Gas]] is put into a [[Condenser]], yielded along with small amounts of [[Crude Oil]] and [[Water]]. [[Fracking Oil]] can be also used to create large yields of '''Water-Free Gas'''. As of {{Update|0.11.3}}, '''Water-Free Gas''' can only be used for the production of [[Refined Gas]].

==Usage==
'''Water-Free Gas''' is use to create [[Refined Gas]], which can either be turned into [[LNG]] in an [[LNG Plant]] for [[Money|Income]] or used in a [[Gas Burner]] to heat [[Water]] for the hottest temperature of [[Steam]] avaliable in the game.

