==Trivia==
*The molecules depicted in the icon are methane (CH<sub>4</sub>), ethane (C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>6</sub>), and propane (C<sub>3</sub>H<sub>8</sub>). Given that the latter two are not outputted from the [[Gas Refinery]], it is heavily implied that they are ejected as [[Residue]].

