{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|research=Water filtering|sellValue={{money|0.55|size=8}}|itemImage=icon-filtered-water.png|resValue={{RP|0.2x }}}}

== Information ==
'''Filtered Water''' is a fluid introduced in {{Update|0.7.0}}. It serves multiple purposes, including the crafting of [[Water Bottle]]s and use in the [[Scrubber]]. During the [[Christmas Event 2023]], '''Filtered Water''' was also usable in the [[Presents Packing Machine]] to double its operational speed.

'''Filtered Water''' is produced by processing regular [[Water]] in a [[Filtration Plant]], which converts four liters of [[Water]] into three liters of '''Filtered Water''' over a duration of two seconds. The reverse processâconverting '''Filtered Water''' back into regular [[Water]] â is supported by the same machine but results in a net loss of Water and is generally inefficient.

== Usage ==
The primary use of '''Filtered Water''' is in the production of [[Water Bottle]]s, which can be sold for profit. While the [[Gearbox]] offers a more efficient source of plastic, [[Water Bottle]]s are simpler to produce and can generate a modest income when properly managed.

A secondary application is in the [[Scrubber]], where '''Filtered Water''' improves the rate of [[Pollution]] removal by 10% compared to regular [[Water]]. This efficiency may reduce the number of [[Scrubber]]s required, though the space occupied by [[Filtration Plant]]s should be considered when evaluating overall viability.

'''Filtered Water''' is also used as a coolant in [[Boiler|Boilers]], increasing steam generation efficiency by 10%. However, due to the low output rate of [[Filtration Plant]]s, maintaining sufficient supply for high-throughput [[Boiler]]s may require significant infrastructure investment.

During the [[Christmas Event 2023]], '''Filtered Water''' could be utilized in the [[Presents Packing Machine]] to double its processing speed. Despite this capability, [[Machine Oil]] was determined to be the more effective option, making '''Filtered Water''' a less popular choice for this purpose.

