{{Item|research=Oil boiling & separating|sellValue={{Money|40.6}}|itemImage=icon-gasoline.png|resValue={{RP|5x }}}}
==Information==
'''Gasoline''' is a type of [[Oil]]/[[Crude Oil]] that only comes from a [[Crude Oil Separator]] or [[Atmospheric Distillation Plant]] as an output. '''Gasoline''' can be used to power the [[Gasoline Generator]] (which contributes to [[pollution]]), to sell at a [[Liquid Truck Depot]], or to be filtered in a [[Filtration Plant]] to make [[Crude Diesel]].

'''Gasoline''' can be a small, effective way of getting some extra power for your [[Oil]] Factory/Plant or something else in your world, by inputting it into a [[Gasoline Generator]]. '''Gasoline''' from the [[Crude Oil Separator]] can also be repurposed in a [[Filtration Plant]] to give a small boost to your [[Crude Diesel]] production if you have no other use for it.

Gasoline can also be turned into [[GasolineE10]] with a [[Chemical Reactor]] and a small amount of [[Ethanol]] which can be sold for decent profit.

