{{Item|itemImage=icon-gear.png|research=Steel|sellValue={{Money|98.6|size=8}}|resValue={{RP|20x }}}}
==Information==

The '''Gear''' is an [[Items|Item]] primarily used in the production of [[Crankshaft|Crankshafts]], which can then be sold or combined with a [[Plastic Casing]] to create a [[Gearbox]]. There are currently no other uses for '''Gears''' other than selling for [[Money]], although most players prefer to sell [[Iron Coil|Iron Coils]] instead.

'''Gears''' can be crafted by inputting [[Steel Plate|Steel Plates]] into a [[Roller]] or [[Press MK2]].

