{{Items Navbox}}

{{Stub}}{{Item|itemImage=icon-gearbox.png|research=Craft Assembler|sellValue={{Money|2,552|size=8}}|resValue={{RP|50x }}}}
==Information==
The '''Gearbox''' is an [[:Category:Items|Item]] designed to be an income source. Alongside its precursor, the [[Crankshaft]], the '''Gearbox''' is seen by players as a bridge between the simplicity of [[Iron Coil|Iron Coils]] and the complex, industrial process needed for [[Purple Gold Ingot|Purple Gold]] and [[Microchip]] production. As such, the '''Gearbox''' fits neatly in between those items in the meta.

The '''Gearbox''' has no other use except as a sellable as of {{Update|1.0}}. It can be produced in either [[Craft Assembler]] or [[Advanced Assembler]] by inputting a [[Crankshaft]] and two [[Plastic Casing|Plastic Casings]], alternatively, the player can also input the [[Steel Rod|Steel Rods]] and [[Gear|Gears]] instead of assembling the [[Crankshaft]], this can be used to cut power consumption, with {{Update|1.0}} introducing [[Hardened Plastic Casing]], the player can replace the standard [[Plastic Casing]] to improve the production rate by four times, with the cost of increased [[Steel Ingot|steel]] consumption.

