==Trivia==
*The '''Gearbox''' in the '''Gearbox''' icon is a gearbox made by [https://pinion.eu/en/technology/ Pinion] for use in bicycles. Despite the '''Gearbox''' in-game using a [[Plastic Casing]] in its recipe, [https://pinion.eu/en/technology/ Pinion] uses [[Aluminium Ingot|Aluminium]] for their '''Gearbox''' casings.
*For some reason, the icon creator (either [[User:Bits.Byte|Bits.Byte]] or [[User:Mamytema|Mamytema]]) used the image that has the gears engaged during 7th gear highlighted instead of the un-highlighted image.
