{{Item|sell_value={{Money|72.50|size=8}}|produced_by_using=[[LNG Plant]]|produced_from=Refined Gas|image1=LNG.jpg|itemImage=icon-lng.png|sellValue={{Money|160|size=8}}|research=LNG Plant|resValue={{RP|2x }}}} ==Information== '''Liquefied natural gas (LNG)''' is a liquid produced in [[LNG Plant]] by converting [[Refined Gas]] into its liquid state. Due to the liquefaction temperature of [[Refined Gas]] resting at approximately {{Heat|-161.5}}, this state of matter switch requires a chunk of power. However, it is still advised to sell '''LNG''', due to its high sell price and lower [[Power]] consumption as of the {{Update|1.0}} update. Note: After the {{Update|0.11.3}} update, the '''LNG's''' sell price dropped from {{Money|174}} to {{Money|160}}.
==Usage== '''LNG''' is an item created purely for selling at the '''LNG Plant''' and is the final step for the [[Refined Gas|Natural Gas]] industry. It requires two [[Liquid Truck Depot|Liquid Truck Depots]] to sell all of the '''LNG''' that one '''LNG Plant''' produces as of {{Update|0.11.3}}. Since its price and yield have been increased, it is seen as a much better way of making money, with a profit rate of {{Money|1,056}}/s per '''LNG Plant''' running at maximum capacity.
Below is a simple ratio for an '''LNG''' setup costing {{Money|2,770,000}}.
