==Trivia== *'''LNG''' is produced by lowering the temperature of [[Refined Gas]] below {{Heat|-161.5}}, thus causing it to liquefy in both in game and in real life. *If '''LNG''' is run through the coolant pipe of a [[Boiler]], it can cause the latter's temperature to drop into the negatives. This is also possible using [[Water]] cooled via the [[Fort-Tech Heavy Cannon MK2]], though the aforementioned machine is restricted to an event. *A completely efficient '''LNG''' farm consumes about{{Power|3.036MMF/s}}. *The molecules shown in the image are [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Methane Methane] molecules. [[Category:Fluids]] {{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|sellValue={{Money|2.9}}|itemImage=Icon-nails.png|research=Roller|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
{{Quote|ð}}
'''Nails''' is an [[Items|Item]] that is typically used to produce [[Chair|Chairs]]. '''Nails''' are produced from [[Iron Ingot|Iron Ingots]] by putting it in a [[Roller]] or [[Industrial Roller]]. It is not recommended to sell '''Nails''' as they do not have a high [[Money|Sell Value]] and are better used to produce [[Chair|Chairs]].

The [[Roller MK2]] cannot create '''Nails''' due it being a coil roller. Chairs are produced by putting [[Planks]] and '''Nails''' either in an [[Craft Assembler]] or an [[Advanced Assembler]].

