{{Item|sellValue={{Money|32.86}}|itemImage=Icon-copper-plate.png|research=Press|resValue={{RP|6x }}}}
==Information==
'''Copper Plate''' is made by inputting [[Copper Ingot]] into a [[Press]]. '''Copper Plates''' are mostly for early game [[Money]] production, production [[Lithium Battery Pack|Lithium Battery Packs]], or [[Logic Plate|Logic Plates]]. 

It is recommended to make [[Copper Wire]], as one '''Copper Plate''' is equal to six [[Copper Wire]], which totals to {{Money|43.86}}, {{Money|11}} dollars greater than '''Copper Plate's''' sell price of {{Money|32.86}}. 

'''Copper Plates''' are also a major component of [[Lithium Battery Pack]], and [[Microchip|Microchips]] being used to make [[Logic Plate|Logic Plates]] in the latter. 

