{{Item|itemImage=Icon-paraxylene.png|research=Plastics|sellValue={{Money|14.5|size=8}}|resValue={{RP|0.2x }}}} ==Information== '''Paraxylene''' or p-Xylene is a liquid chemical that is produced solely by the [[Steam Cracking Plant]] by combining [[Crude Oil]] and [[Steam]] and takes a major role in the production of [[Plastic|Plastics]].
