{{Item|title1=Liquid Iron|tier=2|mined_by_using_=|produced_by_using=|sell_value=|itemImage=Icon-liquid-iron.png|sellValue={{Money|23.2|size=8}}|research=Iron|resValue={{RP|0x }}}}
==Information==
'''Liquid Iron''' is a fluid produced by 3 main ways:

* Processing [[Raw Iron]] in an [[Advanced Electric Furnace|(Advanced)]] [[Electric Furnace]].
* Processing [[Iron Mix]] in an [[Advanced Electric Furnace|(Advanced)]] [[Electric Furnace]].
* Processing [[Treated Raw Iron]] in an [[Industrial Electric Furnace]].

Its main use is to be solidified in an [[Ingot Molder]], as [[Iron Ingot|Iron]] has many more uses while also increasing its value to {{Money|65.54}}.

==Usage==
'''Liquid Iron''' should be turned into [[Iron Ingot|Iron Ingots]] using the [[Ingot Molder]], which can then be turned into a variety of [[Iron Ingot|Iron]] products.

