== Information ==
'''Liquid Copper''' is a liquid metal that is made when inputting [[Raw Copper]] into an [[Electric Furnace]].

==Usage==
'''Liquid Copper''' can be input into an [[Ingot Molder]] to mold and harden it into [[Copper Ingot|Copper Ingots]], which can then be processed into a variety of [[Raw Copper|Copper Products]].

