{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|itemImage=Icon-copper-ingot.png|research=Electric Furnace & Molding|sellValue={{Money|26.68}}|resValue={{RP|1.5x }}}}
==Information==
'''Copper Ingot''' is a item made by an [[Ingot Molder]] when inputted [[Liquid Copper]].

It is important to note that the [[Ingot Molder]] takes two liters of [[Liquid Copper]] to make each '''Copper Ingot'''. It is a good early game source of income, standing at {{Money|26.7}}.

==Usage==
'''Copper Ingot''' farms are good for early game, and when larger even up to early phases of the mid game, and is a good method to use for [[Money]] when the player need to buy more factories.

Do note that with some added cost and complexity, the player can add [[Press|Presses]] and [[Roller|Rollers]] to make [[Copper Wire]], which may not sell for as much but produces a few times more money than [[Raw Copper]].

