{{Item|itemImage=Icon-cut-oak-log.png|research=Sawmill|sellValue={{Money|3.48|size=8}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
The '''Cut Oak Log''' is the refined version of an [[Oak Log]], produced when the latter is run through a [[Sawmill]] or [[Industrial Sawmill]]. It functions as a bridge between the raw [[Oak Log]] and [[Chunk Plank]], having little use on its own.

