{{Item|sellValue={{Money|size=12|3.5}}|research=Sawmill|itemImage=Icon-chunk-plank.png|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
The '''Chunk Plank''' is an item made by running a [[Cut Oak Log]] through a [[Sawmill]] or [[Industrial Sawmill]]. Its sole purpose is to produce [[Planks]]. Its sale highly discouraged.

==Usage==
Due to the '''Chunk Plank's''' abysmal sale value, the only viable use for it is to convert it into [[Planks]] for further use. This is done using another [[Sawmill]] or [[Industrial Sawmill]], as the '''Chunk Plank''' functions to bridge the gap between a [[Cut Oak Log]] and a [[Planks|Plank]].

==Recipes==
{{Production|input1=cut-oak-log|time=10|Mamyflux=0MF|output1=chunk-plank|machine=Industrial Sawmill|Input1Amount=8|Output1Amount=8}}
{{Production|input1=chunk-plank|time=10|Mamyflux=0MF|output1=planks|machine=Industrial Sawmill|Input1Amount=8|Output1Amount=24}}
{{Production|input1=cut-oak-log|time=20|Mamyflux=3kMF|output1=chunk-plank|machine=Sawmill|Input1Amount=1|Output1Amount=1}}
{{Production|input1=chunk-plank|time=20|Mamyflux=3kMF|output1=planks|machine=Sawmill|Input1Amount=1|Output1Amount=3}}

==Trivia==
*Despite being significantly smaller than the [[Cut Oak Log]], the [[Chunk Plank]] still has a {{Ratio|2|1|1}} ratio with the former.
**This is likely due to the debarking process required to convert said [[Cut Oak Log]] into a usable substance.
