{{Item|itemImage=Icon-planks.png|research=Sawmill|sellValue={{Money|13.05|size=8}}|resValue={{RP|5x }}}}
==Information==
{{Quote|Essential material in Chair manufacturing}}
'''Planks''' are an item that is made by running a [[Chunk Plank]] through a [[Sawmill]] or [[Industrial Sawmill]].

==Usage==
The '''Planks''' main purpose is to be crafted into [[Chair|Chairs]] in a [[Craft Assembler]] in combination with [[Nails]].

The ratio to acquire '''Planks''' from [[Sawmill|Sawmills]] is universally {{Ratio|3|1|2|2}} [[Sawmill|Sawmills]], or they can be run through a [[Press]] to get [[Plank^2|Plank<sup>2</sup>]] which is a smaller version of the '''Plank'''.
