==Information==
'''Ethylene''' is a liquid obtained by combining [[Steam]] and [[Crude Oil]] in a [[SteamCrackingPlant|Steam Cracking Plant]]. It sells for the same price as the [[Steam Cracking Plant|Steam Cracking Plant's]] other output, [[Paraxylene]], fetching a price of {{Money|14.5}} per liter. As such, it is not advised to sell [[Ethylene]] unless a surplus of said chemical is present.

