{{Item|tier=3|research=Steel|sellValue={{Money|754}}|title1=Crankshafts|itemImage=icon-crankshaft.png||resValue={{RP|35x }}}}
==Information==
'''Crankshafts''' are an item produced in either the [[Craft Assembler]] or [[Advanced Assembler]] and are composed of two [[Steel Rod|Steel Rods]] and four [[Gear|Gears]]. To unlock the [[Advanced Assembler]], 20 '''Crankshafts''' must be sold beforehand. The '''Crankshaft''' can be combined in either of the two machines listed above with two [[Plastic Casing]] to turn it into a [[Gearbox]], increasing its price and thus making it more profitable.

==Usage==
'''Crankshafts''' can either be sold directly or further processed. To create a [[Gearbox]], one '''Crankshaft'''  must be combined with two [[Plastic Casing|Plastic Casings]] in another [[Craft Assembler]] or [[Advanced Assembler]].

To unlock the [[Advanced Assembler]] in the game, 20 '''Crankshafts''' must be sold, and {{RP|100,000}} must be spent.

==Recipes==
{{Production|input1=steel-rod|Input1Amount=2|input2=gear|Input2Amount=4|time=15|Mamyflux=4kMF|machine=Craft Assembler|output1=crankshaft|Output1Amount=1}}
{{Production|input1=steel-rod|Input1Amount=2|input2=gear|Input2Amount=4|time=5|Mamyflux=200kMF|Output1Amount=1|output1=crankshaft|machine=Advanced Assembler}}
{{Production|input1=plastic-casing|Input1Amount=2|input2=crankshaft|Input2Amount=1|time=15|Mamyflux=4kMF|output1=gearbox|Output1Amount=1|machine=Craft Assembler}}
{{Production|input1=plastic-casing|Input1Amount=2|input2=crankshaft|Input2Amount=1|time=5|Mamyflux=200kMF|output1=gearbox|Output1Amount=1|machine=Advanced Assembler}}

==Trivia==
*Selling a '''Crankshaft''' earns the {{Badge|Just One More Step!}}.

