{{Item|itemImage=Icon-steel-ingot.png|research=Steel|sellValue={{Money|48.72}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Steel Ingots''' are a versatile item made in the [[Blast Furnace]] or [[Blast Furnace MK2]]. '''Steel''' is an essential item throughout the game and is made by putting [[Iron Ingot|Iron Ingots]] or [[Iron Mix]] with [[Coal]] or [[Coke Fuel]] into one of the aforementioned [[Blast Furnace|Blast]] [[Blast Furnace MK2|Furnaces]]. The best way to make '''Steel Ingots''' is via the [[Blast Furnace MK2]] using [[Coke Fuel]] and [[Iron Ingot|Iron Ingots]] from a [[Foundry]].

== Usage ==
As already mentioned, '''Steel Ingot''' has many usages, below are few of its key usage.

* Production of [[Steel Plate|Steel Plates]] and [[Steel Rod|Steel Rods]], these are primarily used for [[Crankshaft|Crankshafts]], which can be further processed into [[Gearbox]].
* Making [[Steel Drill Head]] for the [[Mineshaft Drill]], being one of the most commonly used drill head due to its simplicity and efficiency.

