{{Item|sellValue={{Money|14.5}}|itemImage=Icon-paper.png|research=Paper Mill / Utility|resValue={{RP|7x }}}}
==Information==
'''Paper''' is an item created by a [[Grinder]] combine with [[Water]] or a [[Paper Mill]] using [[Oak Log|Oak Logs]] (''optional for'' [[Chlorine]] ''for more of production''). It is used to make [[Present Box|Present Boxes]] from the [[Craft Assembler]] and is also now used for making [[Filter|Filters]] for the [[Coal Power Plant]].

==Tips==
'''Paper''' can be better made by [[Paper Mill]] instead of [[Grinder]], since it is faster and is more efficient. 

