{{Item|sellValue={{Money|101.5}}|research=Craft Assembler|itemImage=Icon-toy.png|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
A '''Toy''' can be created by inputting [[Black Dye]] and [[Planks]] into the [[Craft Assembler]] or [[Advanced Assembler]]. During the [[Christmas Event 2023|2023 Christmas Event]], it could be used to create [[Packed Present|Packed Presents]] in the [[Presents Packing Machine]], though it can currently only be sold. The '''Toy''' is not recommended for selling as [[Chair|Chairs]] sell for roughly 2.5 times value for the same amount of [[planks]].

