{{Limited}}{{Item|itemImage=2023 12 24 0p7 Kleki.png|sellValue={{money|300}} After Event|research=Unknown|resValue={{RP|Unknown }}}}
==Information==
'''Packed Presents''' can be crafted in the [[Presents Packing Machine]] using [[Toy|Toys]] and [[Present Box|Present Boxes]]. Selling the '''Packed Presents''' is highly discouraged, due to their low sale value and difficulty of production.

As of {{Update|0.11.3}}, selling '''Packed Presents''' will no longer give '''Gifts''', instead providing [[Money]].
{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|sellValue={{money|8.7}}|itemImage=Icon-black-dye.png|research=Utility|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Black Dye''' is a type of rough carbon material which is used in clothing and consumer goods to make another material black colored. It is made from the [[Grinder]] by grinding down [[Coal]].

==Usage==
Black Dye can be used in the [[Craft Assembler]] to produce [[Toy|Toys]], these were mainly used during the [[Christmas Event 2023]] to make the notorious [[Packed Present]]. 

