{{Item|research=Craft Assembler|sellValue={{Money|174|size=8}}|itemImage=Icon-present-box.png|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
The '''Present Box''' is an item added to the [[Christmas Event 2023]] that is made in a [[Craft Assembler]]/[[Advanced Assembler]] using [[Paper]] and [[Black Dye]]. Although related to Christmas Events, this item is not limited and can be made at any time.

===Usage in 2023 Event===
The purpose of a '''Present Box''' in this event was to be a container for a [[Toy]]. This was done using the [[Presents Packing Machine|Present Packing Machine]], and the result was then sold for the [[Present currency (Christmas 2023 event)|Present Currency]], after the event it can be sold for money.

===Usage in 2024 Event===
Akin to the previous year, the '''Present Box''' functioned as a gift container. However, any item could be packaged, though the present's value depended on the contained item value. The [[Advanced Present Packing Machine]] was used for this process, and automatically converted the boxed presents into [[Snowflake Currency]] for use in the event shop.

