{{Item|research=Industrial Electric Furnace|sellValue={{Money|1,000}}|itemImage=Icon-liquid-gold.png|resValue={{RP|0x }}}}
==Information==
'''Liquid Gold''' is a valuable liquid that can be produced by smelting [[Gold]] with an [[Industrial Electric Furnace]]. Higher karats of [[Gold]] produce larger amounts of '''Liquid Gold'''.

==Usage==
'''Liquid Gold''' should be turned into [[Gold Ingot|Gold Ingots]] with an [[Ingot Molder]] to sell, combined with [[Aluminium Ingot|Aluminum]] to make [[Purple Gold Ingot|Purple Gold]] via the [[Alloyer]], or rolled into [[Gold Wire]] for [[Microchip]] production.

It can also be dumped for the {{Badge|What A Waste!}}.

==Recipes==
