|research=Oil Fracking
|sellValue={{Money|65}}
|resValue={{RP|4x }}
}}
==Information==
'''Sulfuric Acid''' is mainly used for [[Gold Ingot|Gold]] Production as it produces [[18 Karat Gold]] straight away when used in a [[Gold Acid Refinery]] when compared to [[Acetic Acid]] but less than [[Hydrochloric Acid]]. '''Sulfuric Acid''' is also used as a replacement for [[Acetic Acid]] in the [[Oil Fracking Tower]] for it uses 7.5L of '''Sulfuric Acid,''' unlike [[Acetic Acid]] which requires 16L. '''Sulfuric acid''' is the most useful acid in the game.

