{{Item|title1=Heavy Oil|itemImage=Icon-heavy-oil.png|caption-itemImage=Its so gosh darn heavy!|tier=3|research=Industrial Diesel Refining|sellValue={{Money|5}}|resValue={{RP|0.2x }}}}
==Information==
[[Heavy Oil]] is a liquid that is produced by an [[Advanced Oil Separator]], [[Atmospheric Distillation Plant]], or [[Coal Liquefaction Plant]] with specific inputs that can be found on their respective [[Recipe Book]] pages. Great for obtaining [[Coke Fuel]] via an [[Advanced Oil Separator]]. It is the best way to produce [[Naphtha]] for [[Rubber]]. Another use for '''Heavy Oil''' is [[Machine Oil]] preferable than filtering [[Refined Diesel]]. 

