==Information==
'''Liquid Sulfur''' is a crucial part of any [[Sulfuric Acid]] production line, as it is a required ingredient of [[Sulfur Dioxide]]. Though acquiring it through the [[Advanced Oil Separator]] is sufficient for a majority of situations, the [[Mineshaft Drill]] is recommended for obtaining such material in large quantities.

