{{Item|itemImage=Icon-sulfur.png|research=Industrial Diesel Refining|sellValue={{Money|30}}|resValue={{RP|12x }}}}
==Information==
'''Sulfur''' is created by inputting [[Liquid Sulfur]] into an [[Ingot Molder]] or by inputting  [[Filtered Water]] and [[Treated Rock]] into a [[Chemical Reactor]]. It sells for {{Money|30}} per unit, making it highly recommended to use the former to use in applications.

== Usage ==
'''Sulfur''' is used to produce [[Sulfur Dioxide]], and later [[Sulfur Trioxide]], to craft the valuable [[Sulfuric Acid]]. Though it sells for a negligible amount of [[Money]], its value shines in its wide variety of applications, causing it to be the most useful acid. It can also be used in the limited [[Cat Assembler]] as an ingredient to create [[Cat]].

