==Trivia==
*'''Sulfur''', alongside [[Ferroaluminium Alloy Ingot|Ferroaluminium Alloy Ingots]], are the only items produced in the [[Ingot Molder]] that do not take the typical shape of an ingot.
*'''Sulfur''' melts at a temperature of {{Heat|235}}.
