{{Item
|title1=Naphtha
|itemImage=Icon-naphtha.png
|research=Oil Fracking
|sellValue={{Money|15.6}}
|resValue={{RP|0.1x }}
}}
==Information==
'''Naphtha''' is produced by inputting [[Fracking Oil]] into the [[Atmospheric Distillation Plant]], being output at a maximum rate of 1.25L/s. It can also be produced in a [[Steam Cracking Plant]] using [[Heavy Oil]] and [[Hydrogen]], and this method uses less power while being simpler, producing 5L/s. 

It can also be produced in small quantities by processing [[Deep Earth Fragment|Deep Earth Fragments]] in the [[Pressurized Water Filter]], although this method is not recommended as it can only yield 0.5L/s of '''Naphtha''' at its maximum rate.  

==Usage==
'''Naphtha's''' main use is to be put into a [[Chemical Reactor]] with [[Heavy Oil]] to make [[Rubber]], a material which can be further processed into [[Tire]] and [[Insulated Wire]].

'''Naphtha''' can also be used to make [[Light Oil]], though it is far outclassed by simply running [[Heavy Oil]] through a [[Steam Cracking Plant]].

