{{Item|title1=Rubber|itemImage=Icon-rubber.png|research=Oil Fracking|sellValue={{Money|19.4}}|resValue={{RP|90x }}}}
==Information==
'''Rubber''' can be made by inputting [[Naphtha]] and [[Heavy Oil]] into a [[Chemical Reactor]], yielding 1.33 units per second at its maximum output. Selling it on its own is highly discouraged, as its low sale value of {{Money|19.4}} renders it not worth the work required to obtain it.

==Usage==
Rubber can be used to make [[Tire|Tires]], [[Insulated Wire]], and [[Lithium Battery Pack|Lithium Battery Packs]], though setting up production lines for anything except the latter is greatly discouraged.

