{{Item|title1=Tire|itemImage=Icon-tire.png|research=Oil Fracking|header1=Information|sellValue={{Money|2,000}}|resValue={{RP|40x }}}}
==Information==
'''Tires''' are made from inputting four units of [[Rubber]] and one [[Tire Rim]] into a [[Craft Assembler]], yielding one '''Tire'''. Producing this item is highly discouraged, as the [[Aluminium Ingot|Aluminium Ingots]] used for making the [[Tire Rim]] can instead be rolled into [[Ferroaluminium Magnet|Ferroaluminium Magnets]], yielding {{Money|2,250}} more than if they were to be processed into '''Tires'''. As such '''Tires''' will likely get a proper use in the future.

==Recipes==
