==Information==
'''Tire Rims''' are produced by inputting two [[Aluminium Ingot|Aluminium Ingots]] and four [[Steel Ingot|Steel Ingots]] into a [[Craft Assembler]] or [[Advanced Assembler]], yielding one '''Tire Rim'''.

==Usage==
'''Tire Rims''' can only be processed further into [[Tire|Tires]] for [[Money]], though it is much more profitable to make [[Ferroaluminium Magnet|Ferroaluminium Magnets]]. 



