==Information==
'''Poor Quality Diesel''' is inferior to [[Diesel]], produced by processing [[Crude Diesel]] in a [[Diesel Refinery]]/[[Industrial Diesel Refinery]].

'''Poor Quality Diesel''' can be used by a [[Large Diesel Engine|Large]]/[[Modular Diesel Engine]] or a [[Diesel Generator]] to produce [[Power]] or sold for [[Money]], but it is much more recommended to further refine the '''Poor Quality Diesel''' by running it through another [[Diesel Refinery]] or [[Industrial Diesel Refinery]] to produce [[Diesel]].

