{{Top-Diesel}}
{{Item|title1=Diesel|itemImage=icon-diesel.png|research=Diesel Refining|sellValue={{Money|30.45|size=8}}|resValue={{RP|2x }}}}
==Information==
'''Diesel''' is the tertiary sector of [[Diesel Refinery|Diesel Production]], made by processing [[Poor Quality Diesel]] in a [[Diesel Refinery]] or [[Industrial Diesel Refinery]], or even by separating [[Light Oil]] in an [[Industrial Oil Separator]] to directly produce '''Diesel'''.

Regular '''Diesel''', like its counterparts, can also be used to generate [[Power]] in a [[Diesel Generator]], [[Modular Diesel Engine]], or a [[Large Diesel Engine]]. It can also be further refined into its pure form, [[Refined Diesel]] which is produced at the end of [[Diesel Refinery|Diesel Refining]].

