{{Top-Diesel}}
{{Item|title1=Crude Diesel|research= Oil boiling & separating|sellValue={{money|13.05|size=8}}|itemImage=Icon-crude-diesel.png|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==

'''Crude Diesel''' is the first step in making [[Refined Diesel]] by putting it into a [[Crude Oil Separator]] to produce [[Crude Diesel]].  

'''Crude Diesel''' is acquired from the [[Crude Oil Separator]] by processing [[Hot Crude Oil]] into it, filtering [[Gasoline]] in the [[Filtration Plant]], or processing [[Light Oil]] in a [[Steam Cracking Plant]]. 

While '''Crude Diesel''' can be sold for [[Money]], it is discouraged due to its low sell price of {{Template:Money|13.05}} as it is recommended to refine it into [[Refined Diesel]] using the [[Diesel Refinery]] (which is unlocked right away), [[Industrial Diesel Refinery]] or [[Advanced Diesel Refinery]] which will result in [[Poor Quality Diesel]] to be produced and [[Residue]] as a byproduct. 

'''Crude Diesel''' can also be burned in a [[Large Diesel Engine|Diesel Generator]], [[Large Diesel Engine]], or [[Modular Diesel Engine]] for power, but it's recommended to refine it into it's better counter parts.

In order to produce [[Refined Diesel]] from '''Crude Diesel''', any of the Diesel refineries must be chained three times. 

