{{Top-Diesel}}
{{Item|title1=Refined Diesel|itemImage=Icon-refined-diesel.png|research=Diesel Refining|sellValue={{Money|40.6|size=8}}|resValue={{RP|3x }}}}
==Information==
'''Refined Diesel''' is the elite level of [[Diesel]] and represents its most refined version. It is produced by refining [[Diesel]] in a [[Diesel Refinery]] or the [[Industrial Diesel Refinery]].

While it is possible to further refine '''Refined Diesel '''into [[Gasoline]], this process is typically impractical because of the same price and for the fact that [[Diesel]] is much more efficient as fuel. However, [[Gasoline]] can be turned into [[GasolineE10]] via a [[Chemical Reactor]], which can yield a greater profit compared to selling the produced '''Refined Diesel''' directly.

This premium-grade [[Diesel]] fuel is primarily used as an input for the [[Modular Diesel Engine|Diesel Generator]], [[Modular Diesel Engine]], and [[Large Diesel Engine]] to generate [[Power]]. It can also be filtered through a [[Filtration Plant]] to produce [[Machine Oil]] or sold. Notably, the [[Modular Diesel Engine]] outputs more [[Power]] per litre of fuel when running with '''Refined Diesel''' as its fuel, making it one of the most lucrative liquids in terms of both energy efficiency and monetary return.

Almost exactly 3/4 (75%) of [[Crude Diesel]] gets turned into   Refined Diesel in the process, resulting in 1/4 (25%) of useless byproduct ([[Residue]]).

==Trivia==
*Further [[Diesel Refinery|refining]] '''Refined Diesel''' converts it into [[Gasoline]] gives the {{Badge|Quality Certified}}.

