{{Item|title1=Gold Wire|tier=3|sellValue={{Money|200}}|itemImage=icon-gold-wire.png|caption-itemImage=|research=Roller|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
== Information ==
Gold wire is  a compressed version of gold, and is made by any type of roller, although the Roller MK2 is the most efficient, and speedy way to create them. It is a crucial, and expensive step in Microchip Production.

== Usage ==
Gold wire only has one usage, and that is in microchip production, as it is a main component in creating them. Although being expensive, the gold wire is over 21x cheaper, but requiring 1 gold ingot per ten wires, being 2x less efficient, it is not recommended to sell.

