{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|itemImage=Icon-graphite-iron-electrode.png|research=Precision Assembler|sellValue={{Money|80}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Graphite-Iron Electrodes''' can be made using: 5 [[Coal|Coals]] and 14 [[Iron Ingot|Iron Ingots]] in the [[Precision Assembler]] to obtain 20 '''Graphite-Iron Electrodes'''. '''Graphite-Iron Electrodes''' are required for the production of [[Uncharged Lithium-Ion|Uncharged Lithium-Ion batteries]] which are then used for [[Lithium Battery Pack]]. 

