{{Item|itemImage=Icon-lithium-carbonate.png|research=Oil fracking|sellValue={{Money|200}}|resValue={{RP|40x }}}}
==Information==
{{Quote|You are now done with the chemistry part}}
'''Lithium Carbonate''' can be synthesized in a [[Chemical Reactor]] from [[Water]], [[Lithium Sulfate]], and [[Sodium Carbonate]]. It sells for {{Money|200}}, though processing it into [[Uncharged Lithium-Ion Battery|Uncharged Lithium-Ion Batteries]] is highly recommended. '''Lithium Carbonate''' is a required ingredient of the latter, a critical item that is needed to obtain [[Lithium Battery Pack|Lithium Battery Packs]] and to thus unlock the [[Logic Assembler]]. 

