{{Item|sellValue={{Money|25}}|itemImage=Icon-lithium-brine.png|research=Lithium/Gold Acid Refinery|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Lithium Brine''' can be obtained by inputting [[Water]] into the [[LithiumBrineExtractor|Lithium Brine Extractor]], yielding '''Lithium Brine''' and [[Residue]]. It is primarily utilized to synthesize [[Dirty Lithium Sulfate]], a substance directly involved in [[Lithium Battery Pack]] production chains. '''Lithium Brine''' is generally regarded as a cheaper, albeit less efficient, alternative to [[Lithium Ore]].

