{{Item|sellValue={{Money|10}}|itemImage=Icon-raw-lead.png|research=Mineshaft Drill|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
[[Raw Lead]] is a raw item excavated from the [[Mineshaft Drill]] or inputting [[Treated Rock|Treated Rocks]] and [[Water]] into a [[Trommel]]. It has only a few recipes, and it sells for only {{Money|10}}, making its excavation needless.

As of {{Update|0.11.3}}, '''Raw Lead''' is only used to make [[Leaded Gasoline]], which sells for {{Money|122}}, and makes {{Power|1MMF}} over 50 seconds in a [[Gasoline Generator]]. Due to requiring a [[Mineshaft Drill]] for meager [[power]] and [[money]], '''Raw Lead''' is not very previlant in the playerbase, and is typically ignored.

The Lead production chain is special in the fact that their recipes are made at a much larger scale as seen in the [[Ingot Molder]] and [[Industrial Electric Furnace]].

