== Trivia ==
* The [[Foundry]] can use '''Raw Lead''' to make [[Lead Ingot|Lead Ingots]], making it one of 3 metals ([[Lead Ingot|Lead]], [[Copper Ingot|Copper]], and [[Iron Ingot|Iron]])  that can be made in the [[Foundry]].
