{{Item|title1=Powdered Tungsten Carbide|tier=3|research=Oil Fracking|sellValue={{money|210}}|itemImage=Icon-powdered-tungsten-carbide.png|caption-itemImage=Very black.|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Powdered Tungsten Carbide''' is the result of inserting 20x [[Hydrogen]] + 4x [[Powdered Tungsten]] + 3x [[Black Dye]] into a [[Chemical Reactor]], and it sells for {{Money|210}}. This powder can be pressed together using a [[Press MK2]] to form [[Tungsten Carbide Plates]], which can then be used to make a [[Tungsten Carbide Drill Head]]. This is the only current way to get the strongest drill head in the game but making it isn't recommended due to its lengthy, costly, and slow process.

