==Information==
The '''Iron Drill Head''' is one of the [[Drill Heads]] available to be used in the [[Mineshaft Drill]].

It can be made in the [[Lathe]], using 2,100 [[Iron Ingot|Iron Ingots]] as the input material taking '''160''' seconds to craft which the '''Iron Drill Head''' will be outputted.

The iron drill head is the second deficient drill head in terms of durability, however not as bad as the copper one, which makes it pretty viable to use.

