==Information==
The '''Tungsten Carbide Drill Head''' is one of the four [[Drill Heads]] available to be used in the [[Mineshaft Drill]]. Akin to all other [[Drill Heads]], it can be made in the [[Lathe]], using 1,275 [[Tungsten Carbide Plates]] as the input material. As the '''Tungsten Carbide Drill Head''' is the strongest [[Drill Heads|Drill Head]] in the game, it takes the longest time to make, with the [[Lathe]] taking four minutes to produce one of the stated.

Due to the difficulty of obtaining [[Tungsten Carbide Plate]], using '''Tungsten Carbide Drill Heads''' in the [[Mineshaft Drill]] is somewhat discouraged. However, the '''Tungsten Carbide Drill Head''' has four times as much durability as the [[Steel Drill Head]].

