==Information==
'''Rock''' is one of the few byproducts of the [[Mineshaft Drill]] and its associated [[Earth Fragments]]. Any produced '''Rock''' can be used for either [[Iron Mix]] or [[Gravel]]. These recipes are useful for [[Filter]] production.

==Usage==
'''Rocks''' can be acquired either through the [[Mineshaft Drill]] or through [[Earth Fragments]]. To find the exact amount of '''Rocks''' the player can obtain through the [[Mineshaft Drill]], the [[Mineshaft Drill/Sheet|Mineshaft Drill Calculator should be used]].

