== Trivia ==

* The name "'''Concentrated Salt Solution'''" is the game's second longest [[Items|Item]] name, sitting at a measly 26 characters, right behind the [[Uncharged Lithium-Ion Battery]], which has a whopping 29 characters.

{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|research=Huge Coal Power Plant|sellValue={{money|0.1}}|itemImage=icon-condensate.png|resValue={{RP|0x }}}}
==Information==
'''Condensate''' is a fluid byproduct produced by the [[Steam Condenser]] after condensing [[Low Pressure Steam]]. After being condensed, '''Condensate''' must be refined in a [[Polisher]], so that the outputted [[Distilled Water]] can be recirculated back into the [[Heat Exchanger]].

One [[Steam Condenser]] can produce up to 800L/s of '''Condensate''', though that output can only be achieved if two [[Coal Power Plant|Coal Power Plants]] are run at once, as a single [[Coal Power Plant]] setup can only yield up to 400L/s of '''Condensate'''.

One [[Polisher]] can refine up to 400L/s of '''Condensate'''. As such, one [[Polisher]] is needed for every [[Coal Power Plant]].

==Usage==
The only use of '''Condensate''' is to be refined in a [[Polisher]] into [[Distilled Water]] so that it can be reused again. Note the ratios and keep a stable supply of [[Hydrochloric Acid]] and [[Sodium Hydroxide Solution|Sodium Hydroxide]] so that the [[Steam Condenser]] does not clog and slow the entire refinement chain to a halt.

==Recipes==
{{Production|input1=condensate|Input1Amount=400|input2=hydrochloric-acid|Input2Amount=1|input3=sodium-hydroxide-solution|Input3Amount=1|time=1|Mamyflux=500kMF|output1=distilled-water|Output1Amount=400|machine=Polisher}}
{{Production|input1=distilled-water|Input1Amount=800|input2=low-pressure-steam|Input2Amount=24000|time=1|Mamyflux=500kMF|output1=distilled-water|Output1Amount=800|output2=condensate|Output2Amount=800|machine=Steam Condenser}}
{{Production|input1=condensate|Input1Amount=64|input2=steam|Input2Amount=363.6ÂºC 90|time=1|Mamyflux=2MMF|output1=distilled-water|Output1Amount=64|machine=Water Treatment Plant}}

