{{Item|title1=Raw Zinc|itemImage=Icon-raw-zinc.png|caption-itemImage=not edible|tier=4|research=Mineshaft Drill|sellValue={{Money|5}}|header1=|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}

==Introduction ==
'''Raw Zinc''' is an ore produced by the [[Mineshaft Drill]] at depths ranging from 4600-4800m. Its direct productâ[[Zinc Sulfate|Zinc Sulphate]]âcan then be further processed into [[Zinc]], [[Galvanized Steel|Galvanised Steel]], [[Liquid Brass]], and [[Graphite-Zinc Electrode|Graphite-Zinc Electrodes.]] However, it is not recommended to produce any of the stated materials, as the first three are ridiculously unprofitable. The fourth product, [[Graphite-Zinc Electrode|Graphite-Zinc Electrodes]], is easily outclassed by [[Graphite-Iron Electrode|Graphite-Iron Electrodes]], due to the latter's ease of production.

