{{Production|input1=acetic-acid|Input1Amount=2|input2=water|Input2Amount=5|input3=medium-earth-fragment|Input3Amount=2|time=5|Mamyflux=100kMF|output1=residue|Output1Amount=4|output2=raw-zinc|Output2Amount=4|machine=Gold Acid Refinery}}{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|title1=Zinc Sulfate|caption-itemImage=ZnSO4|tier=4|research=Chemical Reactor|sellValue={{money|10}}|itemImage=Icon-zinc-sulfate.png|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Zinc Sulfate''' is an [[Items|Item]] produced in a [[Chemical Reactor]] by processing [[Raw Zinc]] and [[Sulfuric Acid]]. It is a critical step in the production of [[Zinc]] and forms the latter when run through an [[Electrolysis Plant]]. In all, it has minimal use only involved in the production of mostly useless products like [[Brass Ingot|Brass]], [[Galvanized Steel]], and [[Graphite-Zinc Electrode|Zinc Electrodes]].

==Trivia==
'''Zinc Sulfate''' is currently the only [[Items|Item]] that can be placed into the [[Electrolysis Plant|Electrolysis Plant's]] [[Items|Item]] input. 

