{{Production|machine=Electrolysis Plant|time=30|Mamyflux=750kMF|output1=zinc|Output1Amount=20|output2=residue|Output2Amount=10|input1=zinc-sulfate|Input1Amount=30}}
{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|research=Ingot Molder|sellValue={{money|80}}|itemImage=Icon-brass-ingot.png|resValue={{RP|35x }}}}
==Information==
'''Brass''' is a material that can only produced by fusing six [[Copper Ingot|Copper Ingots]] and three units of [[Zinc]] in an [[Alloyer]]. The stated machine then produces [[Liquid Brass]], which can be solidified into '''Brass''' in an [[Ingot Molder]]. Each unit of '''Brass''' sells for {{Money|80}}, making it extremely unprofitable when the effort required to synthesize it is taken into account. '''Brass''' has no uses aside from selling, causing it to be a relatively useless item.

==Recipes==
{{Production|input1=liquid-brass|Input1Amount=8|time=4|Mamyflux=150MF|output1=brass-ingot|Output1Amount=4|machine=Ingot Molder}}
{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|title1=Zinc|tier=4|itemImage=Icon-zinc.png|caption-itemImage=Zn|research=Electrolysis plant|sellValue={{money|20|size=8}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
== Information==
'''Zinc''' is a metal [[Items|Item]] that can be produced from processing [[Zinc Sulfate]] in an [[Electrolysis Plant]]. '''Zinc''' can be used to produce three other [[Items]], being the [[Graphite-Zinc Electrode]], [[Liquid Brass]] (then into [[Brass Ingot|Brass]]), and [[Galvanized Steel]]. 

== Usage ==
Producing [[Graphite-Zinc Electrode|Graphite-Zinc Electrodes]] is the most useful [[Recipe Book|Recipe]] of '''Zinc''', being used in [[Lithium Battery Pack]] production, but are overshadowed by [[Graphite-Iron Electrode|Graphite-Iron Electrodes]] due to the latter's easier production chain. 

The other [[Items]] that require '''Zinc''' as a precursor have planned uses in the future that have yet to be worked on.

