{{Item|title1=Treated Raw Iron|research=Chemical Reactor|itemImage=Icon-treated-raw-iron.png|sellValue={{Money|8}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}

==Information==
Obtained with the [[Chemical Reactor]], '''Treated Raw Iron''' is best used in a [[Foundry]] for the mass production of [[Iron Ingot|Iron Ingots]]. One [[Chemical Reactor]] producing '''Treated Raw Iron''' at maximum capacity can support 20 [[Industrial Electric Furnace|Industrial Electric Furnaces]] or 1.82 [[Foundry|Foundries]], thus producing 10 [[Iron Ingot|Iron Ingots]] per second.

