{{Item|title1=Steel Coil|tier=3|research=Roller MK2|sellValue={{money|75}}|caption-itemImage=Death Coil|itemImage=Icon-steel-coil.png|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
== Information ==
'''Steel Coils''' are a tier 3 item made exclusively from the [[Roller MK2]]. Instead of making [[Steel Rod|Steel Rods]] like in the normal [[roller]], the [[Roller MK2]] makes '''Steel coils''' for selling. If the player wants to turn '''Steel Coils''' into [[Steel Rod|Steel rods]], they must put Steel Coils into the [[Lathe]]. Making [[Steel Rod|Steel Rods]] using the [[Lathe]] makes 2x fewer [[Steel Rod|Steel Rods]] per [[Steel Ingot]] than using the regular [[Roller]].

