{{Item|research=Chemical Reactor|sellValue={{money|6}}|itemImage=Icon-treated-raw-copper.png|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Treated Raw Copper''' is an item obtained by inputting [[Raw Copper]] and [[Hydrochloric Acid]] into a [[Chemical Reactor]]. The recipe is the same as the one for [[Treated Raw Iron]], but it uses [[Raw Copper]] instead. As of {{Update|0.11.3}}, the only viable use for '''Treated Raw Copper''' is for mass production in the [[Foundry]], as it requires 1,600 less [[Raw Copper]]. This method yelds the same amount of [[Copper Ingot|Copper Ingots]] produced, with the only major cost being 20 liters of [[Hydrochloric Acid]] per cycle. The player can also input it into [[Industrial Electric Furnace|Industrial Electric Furnaces]] if the player does not have a good [[Coke Fuel]] setup. One [[Chemical Reactor]] can support 1.82 [[Foundry|Foundries]] or 20 [[Industrial Electric Furnace|Industrial Electric Furnaces]].

Ratios for the [[Industrial Electric Furnace]] set up would be {{Ratio|3|1|20|20}} ([[Chemical Reactor]] : [[Industrial Electric Furnace]] : [[Ingot Molder]]) making 10 [[Copper Ingot|Copper Ingots]] per second.

