{{Item|title1=Low Pressure Steam|caption-itemImage=|tier=4|research=Modular Turbine|header1=|sellValue={{money|0.03}}|itemImage=icon-low-pressure-steam.png|resValue={{RP|0x }}}}
==Information==
'''Low Pressure Steam''' is a waste fluid that is the byproduct of the [[Modular Turbine]]. It is '''HIGHLY HIGHLY''' recommended to run this through a [[Steam Condenser]] and [[Polisher]] to recirculate it as [[Distilled Water]] back into a [[Heat Exchanger]] to be reused in the [[Modular Turbine]] as [[High Pressure Steam]]. Not only is this because it is better than making new [[Distilled Water]] but selling '''Low Pressure Steam''' would require tons of [[Large Liquid Truck Depot|Large Liquid Truck Depots]] and [[Pipes|Pipe Converters]], and would sell for next to nothing. '''Low Pressure Steam''' is shortened to '''LPS''' in the [[Coal Power Plant|Coal Power Plant's]] external data panel. In [[Sandbox]] mode, players can use the [[Large Gold Fluid Storage Silo]] to contain '''Low Pressure Steam'''.

==Recipes==
{{Production|input1=distilled-water|Input1Amount=800|input2=low-pressure-steam|Input2Amount=24000|time=1|Mamyflux=500kMF|machine=Steam Condenser|output1=distilled-water|Output1Amount=800|output2=condensate|Output2Amount=800}}

==Trivia==
*The Recipe for '''Low Pressure Steam''' is not listed in the [[Recipe Book]]. This is because the condenser recipe uses [[Steam]] instead of '''Low Pressure Steam''' even though it cannot condense regular [[Steam]] from boilers.
{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|itemImage=Icon-high-pressure-steam.png|research=Huge Coal Power Plant|sellValue={{money|0.03}}|resValue={{RP|0x }}}}
==Information==
'''High Pressure Steam''' is a fluid that is used in the [[Modular Turbine]]. It is essential for late game [[Power]] generation and can be made by a [[Heat Exchanger]] or [[Heat Exchanger|Vertical Heat Exchanger]] using [[Distilled Water]] and hot [[Distilled Water]] coolant. One [[Heat Exchanger]] can only make 12kL/s of '''High Pressure Steam''' so two [[Heat Exchanger|Heat Exchangers]] must be used in order to reach the [[Modular Turbine|Modular Turbine's]] maximum capacity of 24kL/s. '''High Pressure Steam''' is labeled as '''HPS''' in the [[Coal Power Plant|Coal Power Plant's]] external data panel.

==Recipes==
{{Production|input1=distilled-water|Input1Amount=400|input2=distilled-water|Input2Amount=400|time=1|Mamyflux=0MF|machine=Heat Exchanger|output1=distilled-water|Output1Amount=400|output2=high-pressure-steam|Output2Amount=12000}}
{{Production|input1=contaminated-water|Input1Amount=400|input2=distilled-water|Input2Amount=400|time=1|Mamyflux=0MF|machine=Heat Exchanger|output1=contaminated-water|Output1Amount=400|output2=high-pressure-steam|Output2Amount=12000}}
{{Production|input1=distilled-water|Input1Amount=400|input2=distilled-water|Input2Amount=400|time=1|Mamyflux=0MF|machine=Vertical Heat Exchanger|output1=distilled-water|Output1Amount=400|output2=high-pressure-steam|Output2Amount=12000}}
{{Production|input1=contaminated-water|Input1Amount=400|input2=distilled-water|Input2Amount=400|time=1|Mamyflux=0MF|machine=Vertical Heat Exchanger|output1=contaminated-water|Output1Amount=400|output2=high-pressure-steam|Output2Amount=12000}}


==Trivia==
*'''High Pressure Steam''' has no recipes in the [[Recipe Book]] as they are replaced by normal [[Steam]], even though the [[Heat Exchanger]] and [[Vertical Heat Exchanger]] cannot produce normal [[Steam]].
