'''8 Karat Gold''' is the lowest quality of [[Gold]] that can be made, and is usually not very profitable. This karat of [[Gold]] comes only from refining [[Rich Soil]] in the [[Pressurized Water Filter]].

Price increase since last karat is: +0%

==Usage==
Cannot be upgraded to the next quality of karat, however it can be smelted directly by the [[Industrial Electric Furnace]] to be later turned into [[Gold Ingot|Gold Ingots]]. However, this happens at an extremely slow speed, so it is much more advised to make [[10 Karat Gold]].

