'''12 Karat Gold''' is the point where gold starts becoming golden. This karat of [[Gold]] comes only from processing [[10 Karat Gold]] in the [[Pressurized Water Filter]]. This [[Gold]] quality also has no difference from [[10 Karat Gold]], other than a {{Money|200}} sale increase.

Price increase since last karat is: +66%

==Usage==
To be put into the [[Gold Acid Refinery]] which refines it to its more refined sister, [[18 Karat Gold]], or it can be smelted into [[Liquid Gold]] using the [[Industrial Electric Furnace]].

