'''24 Karat Gold''' is the best variant of [[Gold]] to process from its long line of inferior [[Gold]] tiers. It is refined by the [[Pressurized Water Filter]], and is highly recommended due to its increase in [[Liquid Gold]] yield after refining [[18 Karat Gold]].

Price increase since last karat is: +50%

==Usage==
Can only be sold or further processed into [[Liquid Gold]] by the [[Industrial Electric Furnace]] for higher purposes of producing the [[Purple Gold Ingot]].

