{{Limited}}
{{Item|sellValue={{Money|20,000|size=8}}|research=None|itemImage=Icon-cat.png|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
The '''Cat''' is an item produced in the [[Cat Assembler]]. It is an event item from the [[April fools 2025|April Fool's 2025 event]].

==Usage==
Despite selling for the same amount as a [[Purple Gold Ingot]], at {{Money|20,000}}, it is not a worthwhile method of generating [[Money]]. This is due to the [[Cat Assembler|Cat Assembler's]] lengthy assembly time and complex production chain. While the [[Cat Assembler]] itself consumes no [[Power]] and releases zero [[Pollution]], the amount of machines required for producing the [[Electric Motor|Electric Motors]] alone would far outweigh this slight benefit.

==Recipes==
{{Production|input1=gasoline|Input1Amount=31|input2=electric-motor|Input2Amount=4|input3=sulfur|Input3Amount=15|time=92|Mamyflux=Maxwell|output1=cat|Output1Amount=1|machine=Cat Assembler}}

== Trivia ==

* '''Cat''' is a reference to the meme [https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/original/002/496/287/ac2.jpg Maxwell].
{{Items Navbox}}

{{Hatnote}}
{{Item
|itemImage=Icon-yellowcake.png
|title1=Yellowcake
|sellValue={{Money|0|size=8}}
|research=Advanced Oxidation Plant
|resValue={{RP|5x }}}}
== Information ==
'''Yellowcake''' is a resource that is required for the [[Nuclear Power Plant]]. It can be processed into [[MOX Fuel Rod]] and [[Low Enrichment Fuel Rod]] via the [[Precision Assembler]]. This resource should not be extracted unless you are trying to create a [[Nuclear Power Plant]], as it has a sell value of {{Money|0}}. Contrary to what some people might have believed, this resource does not have any connection to [[Uranium]], due to [[Uranium]] being a joke item. Instead, '''Yellowcake''' is created using [[Mixed Uranium Oxides]], [[Sulfuric Acid]], with either [[Oxygen]] or [[Ammonia]], in an [[Advanced Oxidation Plant]].

== Usage ==
'''Yellowcake''' is processed into [[MOX Fuel Rod]] and [[Low Enrichment Fuel Rod]] via the [[Precision Assembler]] by adding [[Zirconium Rod]] for [[MOX Fuel Rod]] and additionally adding [[Plutonium Oxide Pellets]] for [[Low Enrichment Fuel Rod]], which are crucial for the [[Nuclear Power Plant]] to run. It can also be processed into [[Unenriched UF6 Gas]] via the [[Chemical Plant]] by adding [[Hydrochloric Acid]]. The [[Unenriched UF6 Gas]] can be enriched in [[Chemical Plant]] multiples times until [[Enriched UF6 Gas]], where enriching it further with [[Steam]] and either [[Hydrogen]] or [[Tributyl Phosphate]] will form [[Enriched UO2 Pellets]] which can be made into [[Standard Fuel Rod]] by combining it with [[Zirconium Rod]] using the [[Precision Assembler]].

== Recipes ==
{{production|input1=mixed-uranium-oxides|Input1Amount=10|input2=oxygen|Input2Amount=100|input3=sulfuric-acid|Input3Amount=100|time=40|Mamyflux=1MMF|output1=yellowcake|Output1Amount=4|machine=Advanced Oxidation Plant}}
{{production|input1=mixed-uranium-oxides|Input1Amount=10|input2=ammonia|Input2Amount=10|input3=sulfuric-acid|Input3Amount=100|time=40|Mamyflux=1MMF|output1=yellowcake|Output1Amount=8|machine=Advanced Oxidation Plant}}
{{production|input1=zirconium-rod|Input1Amount=1|input2=plutonium-oxide-pellets|Input2Amount=20|input3=yellowcake|Input3Amount=10|time=5|Mamyflux=1MMF|output1=mox-fuel-rod|Output1Amount=1|machine=Precision Assembler}}
{{production|input1=zirconium-rod|Input1Amount=1|input2=yellowcake|Input2Amount=30|time=5|Mamyflux=1MMF|output1=low-enrichment-fuel-rod|machine=Precision Assembler|Output1Amount=1}}
{{production|input1=yellowcake|Input1Amount=0.5|input2=hydrofluoric-acid|Input2Amount=0.5|time=1|Mamyflux=500kMF|output1=unenriched-uf6-gas|Output1Amount=1.5|machine=Chemical Plant}}{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item
|itemImage=Icon-clay.png
|research=Quarry
|sellValue={{Money|2}}
|resValue={{RP|0.2x}}
}}
==Information==
'''Clay''' is dugged up by powering a [[Quarry]]. It is necessary in producing [[Brick|Bricks]]. The production of '''Clay''' can be doubled by inputting [[Water]] Into a [[Quarry]]. Clay is also a necessity in producing [[Rawmix]].

== Usage ==
'''Clay''' is used in Brick production, being the main, and often only ingredient in [[Clay Brick|Clay Bricks]]. Clay bricks can also be Placed into a [[Concrete Plant]]. Producing '''Clay''' to form [[Clay Brick|Clay Bricks]], to then, further Process into [[Brick|Bricks]], which are an excellent early-mid game income source.

