==Information==
'''Bricks''' are produced in a [[Kiln]], by heating the [[Clay Brick|Clay Bricks]], The [[Water]] evaporates, forming a hard structure.

== Usage ==
As of {{Update|0.1v}} '''Bricks''' only purpose is to be sold, Because of their high sell value.

