[[Category:Items]]
{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|itemImage=Icon-clay-brick.png|research=Brick Production|sellValue={{Money|28}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
'''Clay Brick''' is a stepping stone for the eventual [[Brick]]. '''Clay Bricks''' have no use other than to create them. The player can create more '''Clay Bricks''' by utilizing different items, such as [[Limestone]] or [[Iron Powder]]. It is more beneficial to use [[Iron Powder]] as the output doubles from 10 to 20.

== Usage ==
'''Clay Bricks''' have the [[Water]] evaporated in a [[Kiln]], to be Processed into [[Brick|Bricks]].

