== Information ==
{{Quote|Obtained from mineshaft drill at deep levels.}}
'''Raw Zirconium''' is an ore obtained from the [[Mineshaft Drill]] between 8200 meters and 8600 meters and also at 9000 meters of depth. It's recommended to mine at 8400m for the Raw Zirconium.

== Usage ==
'''Raw Zirconium''' is used in the production of nuclear fuel for the [[Nuclear Power Plant]]. It's one of the first items in the nuclear branch. Combine it with [[Chlorine]] to obtain [[Zirconium Chloride]] ( [[Residue]] is the waste of the process).

== Recipe ==
{{Production|input1=chlorine|time=4|Mamyflux=750kMF|output1=zirconium-chloride|machine=Chemical Reactor|Input1Amount=2|Output1Amount=4|input2=raw-zirconium|Input2Amount=2|output2=residue|Output2Amount=1}}

