==Information==
{{Quote|Aggregate muncher.}}
'''Aggregate''' Is made from inputting [[Gravel]] into the [[Raw Mill]], Like [[Rawmix]], it can be produced alongside eachother, or  individually.

== Usage ==
[[Aggregate]] is used to make Wet concrete, Like [[Rawmix]] it is used in Concrete Production, but coming after.

