{{Item|title1=Limestone|itemImage=Icon-limestone.png|research=Quarry|sellValue={{Money|1}}}}
==Information==
'''Limestone''' is produced by the [[Quarry]]. Limestone is a versatile resource, as the uses it has differ wildly from each other. Like all other materials produced by the [[Quarry]], '''Limestone''' can be doubled by inserting [[Water]] into a [[Quarry]].

==Usage==
There are many uses of '''Limestone''', such as being a main ingredient in producing [[Rawmix]], a step in [[Concrete]] production, it can also be used in boosting the output of the [[Concrete Plant|Concrete Plant's]] [[Clay Brick]] Production. By far its most important use for endgame is being an ingredient in [[Mixed Fissile Oxides]]

