{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|itemImage=Icon-zirconium-dioxide.png|research=Chemical Reactor|sellValue={{Money|45}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}

== Information ==
'''Zirconium Dioxide''' is obtained from processing [[Distilled Water]] and [[Zirconium Chloride]] in a [[Chemical Reactor]], and is required to make [[Zirconium Rod|Zirconium Rods]]. 

== Usage ==
Has only one use, apart from selling, which is to make [[Zirconium Rod|Zirconium Rods]] inside an [[Industrial Roller]].

