{{Items Navbox}}

{{Stub}}{{Item|itemImage=Icon-liquid-oxygen.png|research=Air Separation Unit|sellValue={{Money|6}}|resValue={{RP|3x }}}}

== Information ==
'''Liquid Oxygen''' is one of the three fluids that is produced through an [[Air Separation Unit]], producing 3 liters every second. It is the warmest fluid amongst the three fluids such as [[Liquid Nitrogen]] and [[Liquid Argon]], with a temperature to as low as -170Â°C.

When producing [[Oxygen]] gas, this is generally the best method to produce it, as the latter can produce up to 90 liters of Oxygen every second, in contrast to the [[Electrolysis Plant]], which produces only 1 liter of Oxygen every second.

== Usage ==
Liquid Oxygen currently only has one use, and it is to change the state of the element into gas, [[Oxygen]]. Around 5 [[Vaporizer|Vaporizers]] is needed to supply the demand of Liquid Oxygen. Anything more or less may become inefficient or clog up the [[Air Separation Unit]], potentially disabling the machine.

== Recipes ==
{{Production|time=1|Mamyflux=20MMF|output1=liquid-nitrogen|Output1Amount=60|output2=liquid-oxygen|Output2Amount=15|output3=liquid-argon|output4=residue|Output4Amount=?|Output3Amount=3|machine=Air Separation Unit}}
{{Production|time=1|Mamyflux=15kMF|input1=liquid-oxygen|Input1Amount=3|output1=oxygen|Output1Amount=90|machine=Vaporizer}}

