'''Liquid Nitrogen''' is one of the three fluids that is produced through an [[Air Separation Unit]], producing 3 liters every second. It is the coldest fluid amongst the three fluids such as [[Liquid Argon]] and [[Liquid Oxygen]], with a temperature to as low as -205Â°C.

