{{Stub}}{{Item|itemImage=Icon-liquid-argon.png|research=Air Separation Unit|sellValue={{Money|50}}|resValue={{RP|3x }}}}

== Information ==
'''Liquid Argon''' is one of the three fluids that is produced through an [[Air Separation Unit]], producing 3 liters every second. It is the second-coldest fluid amongst the three fluids such as [[Liquid Nitrogen]] and [[Liquid Oxygen]], with a temperature to as low as -195Â°C.

== Usage ==
'''Liquid Argon''' currently only has one use, and it is to change the state of the element into gas, [[Argon]]. Only 1 [[Vaporizer]] is needed to supply the demand of Liquid Argon. Anything more than one vaporizer may become inefficient.

== Recipes ==
