{{Stub}}{{Item|title1=Mixed Fissile Oxides|itemImage=Icon-mixed-fissile-oxides.png|research=Advanced Oxidation Plant|sellValue={{Money|0}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
[[Mixed Fissile Oxides]] are an end-game nuclear material produced in the [[Advanced Oxidation Plant]]. They are used in late-game nuclear processing and are an important ingredient for crafting advanced nuclear fuels.

==Usage==
[[Mixed Fissile Oxides]] are used in the [[Chemical Plant]] to produce [[Reprocessed Uranium]] and [[Plutonium Oxide Pellets]]. During this process, [[Residue]] is also created as a byproduct.

