{{Top-fuel-rods}}{{Stub}}{{Item|title1=MOX Fuel Rod|sellValue={{Money|1000000}}|itemImage=Icon-mox-fuel-rod.png|research=Precision Assembler|resValue={{RP|100x }}}}

== Information ==
The '''MOX Fuel Rod''' is an item used in the [[Nuclear Power Plant]]. It is the most complex fuel rod to create, requiring 3 items. It can last for up to 70 hours before running out, far greater than other fuel rods.

== Usage ==
When spent, the '''MOX Fuel Rod''' is turned into [[Spent MOX Fuel]], which has no practical use and cannot be reprocessed, so it must be stored in the [[Underground Waste Facility]].

