== Information ==
The '''Standard Fuel Rod''' is an item used in the [[Nuclear Power Plant]] and requires refining of raw uranium in order to create. This item is the 2nd longest lasting fuel rod with a lifetime of about 35 hours.

== Usage ==
When spent, the item will be converted into [[Spent Fuel]], which can either be stored in the [[Underground Waste Facility]] or reprocessed into other materials.

