== Information ==
'''Control Rod''' used in the [[Nuclear Power Plant]] core to maintain temperature by rising or lowering.

== Usage ==
'''Control Rod''' are used to regulate [[Nuclear Power Plant]] core by absorbing neutrons to control the rate of the chain reaction with in the [[Nuclear Power Plant]].

