{{Stub}}
{{Item|title1=Zirconium Rod|itemImage=Icon-zirconium-rod.png|sellValue={{Money|180}}|research=Industrial Roller|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}

== Information ==
The '''Zirconium Rod''' serves as a base component for the production of all [[Fuel Rod]]s and [[Control Rod]]s. It is required in multiple crafting recipes related to nuclear energy. 

While producing '''Zirconium Rods''' can be relatively easy, it is not advised to produce them in large quantities, unless they are to be used to make [[Fuel Rod]]s for constructing a [[Nuclear Power Plant]].

== Usage ==
The '''Zirconium Rod''' is used in the creation of the [[Standard Fuel Rod|Standard Fuel Rods]], [[Control Rod|Control Rods]], [[MOX Fuel Rod|MOX Fuel Rods]], and [[Low Enrichment Fuel Rod|Low Enrichment Fuel Rods]]. It is an essential component in nuclear fuel assembly and reactor control systems.

