==Information==
The '''Hardened Plastic Casing''' is an alternative to the [[Plastic Casing]] made in the [[Industrial Plastic Molder]] that can be used in the same way as the [[Plastic Casing]]. The '''Hardened Plastic Casing''' takes lesser [[Hardened Plastic Pellets]] compared to the [[Plastic Casing]], but has a significantly harder recipe in exchange, requiring [[Naphtha]] and [[Ammonia]] to be made.

==Usage==
The '''Hardened Plastic Casing''' is used to produce [[Uncharged Lithium-Ion Battery]] as a replacement to [[Plastic Pellet]]s in the recipe, and as a [[Plastic Casing]] replacement in the production of [[Gearbox]]es in the [[Advanced Assembler]], requiring more [[Items]] in general as the recipe for producing [[Gearbox]]es using the '''Hardened Plastic Casing''' uses four [[Steel Rod]]s and eight [[Gear]]s and having an five seconds cycle time.

