{{Item|title1=Mixed Fissile Nitrates|itemImage=Icon-mixed-fissile-nitrates.png|research=Ore Enrichment Facility|sellValue={{Money|0}}|resValue={{RP|1x }}}}
==Information==
[[Mixed Fissile Nitrates]] are a processed nuclear material created in the [[Ore Enrichment Facility]]. They are the only way to produce [[Mixed Fissile Oxides]], making them an important step in advanced nuclear refining.
==Usage==
[[Mixed Fissile Nitrates]] are mainly used to create [[Mixed Fissile Oxides]] in the [[Advanced Oxidation Plant]]. During the conversion process, additional materials such as [[Fission Byproduct]]s and [[Residue]] are also produced.
