{{Production|input1=reprocessed-uranium|Input1Amount=0.5|input2=hydrofluoric-acid|Input2Amount=0.5|time=1|Mamyflux=100kMF|output1=slightly-enriched-uf6-gas|Output1Amount=2|machine=Chemical Plant}}
