== Information ==
'''Mixed Uranium Oxides''' are one of the main products of the [[Ore Enrichment Facility]]. They are used in the production of [[Yellowcake]], a stepping stone in Nuclear Power.

== Usage ==
As mentioned before, '''Mixed Uranium Oxides''' are used in the production of [[Yellowcake]], through the [[Advanced Oxidation Plant]] using [[Oxygen]] or [[Ammonia]] with [[Sulfuric Acid]]. However, it is a very expensive recipe requiring 100 of each ingredient excluding the '''Mixed Uranium Oxides''' themselves, where only ten are required.

