{{Stub}}
{{Item
|title1=Spent Fuel
|itemImage=Icon-spent-fuel.png
|sellValue={{Money|-1000000}}
|resValue={{RP|0x }}|research=Nuclear Power Plant}}
== Information ==
'''Spent Fuel''' is produced by operating the [[Nuclear Power Plant]]. Due to its high radioactivity, it can only be safely stored in the [[Underground Waste Facility]] or sent for reprocessing to recover usable [[Mixed Fissile Nitrates|Fissile Materials]]. It cannot be stored in [[Gold Item Storage Silo|Silos]].

== Usage ==
'''Spent Fuel''' can be used to produce [[Mixed Fissile Nitrates]], which are further processed into materials required for nuclear fuel recycling. This eventually enables the creation of [[MOX Fuel Rod|MOX Fuel Rods]].

== Recipes ==
{{Production|input1=spent-fuel|Input1Amount=50|input2=hydrochloric-acid|Input2Amount=1|input3=nitrogen|Input3Amount=120|time=10|Mamyflux=500kMF|output1=mixed-fissile-nitrates|Output1Amount=5|output2=fission-byproducts|Output2Amount=95|output3=residue|Output3Amount=5|machine=Ore Enrichment Facility}}
{{Production|input1=spent-fuel|Input1Amount=50|input2=sulfuric-acid|Input2Amount=1|input3=nitrogen|Input3Amount=120|time=10|Mamyflux=500kMF|output1=mixed-fissile-nitrates|Output1Amount=7|output2=fission-byproducts|Output2Amount=93|output3=residue|Output3Amount=10|machine=Ore Enrichment Facility}}

