{{Top-uf6}}{{Stub}}
{{Item
|itemImage=Icon-depleted-uf6-waste.png
|sellValue={{Money|-250}}
|research=Centrifuge
|resValue={{RP|0x }}
}}
==Information==
{{Quote|It is slightly radioactive, so should be stored underground in the Underground Waste Facility.}}
Depleted UF6 Waste is a byproduct of creating [[Slightly Enriched UF6 Gas]] or [[Enriched UF6 Gas]] in the [[Gas Centrifuge]]. It is slightly [[Radiation|Radioactive]] and can not be processed further so it should be stored in a [[Underground Waste Facility]].

== Usage ==
As mentioned before, this [[Items|Fluid]] doesn't have use and is slightly [[Radiation|Radioactive]], so it must be stored in the [[Underground Waste Facility]] to prevent [[Radiation]] from affecting a player's world. Selling it is also not recommended as loading it into a [[Liquid Truck Depot]] would result in a loss of {{Money|-100,000}} per sell.

==Recipes==
{{Production|input1=unenriched-uf6-gas|Input1Amount=0.5|time=1|Mamyflux=1MMF|output1=depleted-uf6-waste|Output1Amount=0.1|output2=slightly-enriched-uf6-gas|Output2Amount=0.1|output3=unenriched-uf6-gas|Output3Amount=0.25|machine=Gas Centrifuge}}{{Production|input1=slightly-enriched-uf6-gas|Input1Amount=0.5|time=1|Mamyflux=1MMF|output1=depleted-uf6-waste|Output1Amount=0.1|output2=enriched-uf6-gas|Output2Amount=0.05|output3=slightly-enriched-uf6-gas|Output3Amount=0.3|machine=Gas Centrifuge}}

==Trivia==
* '''Depleted UF6 Gas''' is also known as Depleted uranium hexafluoride, and much like real life, it is a byproduct of processing [[Slightly Enriched UF6 Gas|UF6 Gas]] (or Uranium hexafluoride gas) into [[Enriched UF6 Gas|Enriched Uranium]].
* This is one of the few [[Items|Fluids]] that have a negative sell value, being 89.3 times more than the sell value of [[Residue]].
