==Information==
'''Hardened Plastic Pellets''' is a product that are manufactured using 25 liters of [[Ammonia]] and 5 liters of [[Naphtha]] via the [[Chemical Plant]]. It is the upgraded and refined version to that of a standard [[Plastic Pellets]], thought has no crafting recipe to produce the hardened version of [[Plastic Bottle|Plastic Bottles]]. 

Despite the cost and research node(s) required to even grant its function to be produced, it is slightly less complex to craft than the regular [[Plastic Pellets]].

==Usage==
As of {{Update|1.0}}, this material only has one use, and is to be inputted into the [[Industrial Plastic Molder]] machine in order to manufacture [[Hardened Plastic Casing]]. 

==Recipes==
