== Information ==
Slightly Enriched UF6 Gas is the product of either enriching [[Unenriched UF6 Gas]] in the [[Gas Centrifuge]] or combining [[Reprocessed Uranium]] and [[Hydrofluoric Acid]] in the [[Chemical Plant]]

== Usage ==
The only use of Slightly Enriched UF6 Gas is to enrich it further in the Gas Centrifuge and produce [[Enriched UF6 Gas]] which can later be used to create [[Enriched UO2 Pellets]]. Selling it is not recommended as Slightly Enriched UF6 Gas only sells for {{Money|45}} per unit.

