== Information ==
'''Unenriched UF6 Gas''' is a stepping stone in creating [[Enriched UO2 Pellets]] and then [[Standard Fuel Rod]]. It is a product of processed [[Yellowcake]] and [[Hydrofluoric Acid]] inside the [[Chemical Plant]].

== Usage ==
The only usage '''Unenriched UF6 Gas''' has is to be enriched into [[Slightly Enriched UF6 Gas]], selling it is not recommended as it only gives {{Money|30}} per unit and creating it for any other purposes except for [[Standard Fuel Rod]] manufacturing is also not recommended.

== Recipe ==
{{Production|input1=unenriched-uf6-gas|Input1Amount=0.5|time=1|Mamyflux=1MMF|output1=depleted-uf6-waste|Output1Amount=0.1|output2=slightly-enriched-uf6-gas|Output2Amount=0.1|output3=unenriched-uf6-gas|Output3Amount=0.25|machine=Gas Centrifuge}}
