== Trivia ==
* This item was added in {{Update|1.0}}.
* UF6 is a chemical formula for Uranium hexafluoride, which is a combination of Uranium and Fluorine used for enriching Uranium for nuclear reactors and nuclear weapons.
* The icon represents actual UF6 Atoms.
