== Information ==
Enriched UF6 Gas is the final product of the [[Gas Centrifuge]], it is obtained by enriching [[Unenriched UF6 Gas]] and then enriching [[Slightly Enriched UF6 Gas]] in the Gas Centrifuge.

== Usage ==
Enriched UF6 Gas is used to create [[Enriched UO2 Pellets]] with either [[Tributyl Phosphate]] or [[Hydrogen]] which are then used to create [[Standard Fuel Rod|Standard Fuel Rods]], it has no other use beyond that, selling is also not recommended as the production of even one unit of Enriched UF6 gas will take a long time since only 0.05 units of UF6 gas are being output per second, which means it would take around 20 seconds for 1 unit of Enriched UF6 Gas. And also because it sells for measly {{Money|150}}.

