{{Stub}}{{Item|itemImage=Icon-tributyl-phosphate.png|research=Advanced Chemical Plant|sellValue={{Money|0}}|resValue={{RP|0x }}}}

== Information ==
'''Tributyl Phosphate''' (C<sub>12</sub>H<sub>27</sub>O<sub>4</sub>P) is a substance made from [[Phosphorus Oxychloride]], [[Ethanol]], and [[Steam]]. It is used in Nuclear Fuel production.

== Usage ==

It is used as a better alternative to [[Oxygen]] in making [[Mixed Fissile Oxides]], and a better alternative to [[Hydrogen]] in making [[Enriched UO2 Pellets]].
