{{Stub}}{{Item|itemImage=Icon-plutonium-oxide-pellets.png|sellValue={{Money|1250}}|resValue={{RP|0x }}|research=Advanced Chemical Plant, Nuclear Power Plant}}
== Information == '''Plutonium Oxide Pellets''' is a resource that is required to produce [[MOX Fuel Rod|MOX Fuel Rods]] for the [[Nuclear Power Plant]]. It is composed of several ingredients such as [[Mixed Fissile Oxides]], [[Hydrochloric Acid]], [[Sodium Hydroxide Solution]], and [[Argon]] and is inputted via the [[Chemical Plant]]. This material is vital, as this is the only method known to produce [[MOX Fuel Rod|MOX Fuel Rods]] as of {{Update|1.0}}.
Obtaining '''Plutonium Oxide Pellets''' without having to produce [[Spent Fuel]] from a [[Standard Fuel Rod]] or [[Low Enrichment Fuel Rod]] is rendered as impossible. This is due to the latter requiring [[Mixed Fissile Oxides]], which are produced from [[Mixed Fissile Nitrates]] that are originated from [[Spent Fuel]].
== Usage == As mentioned, the primary use of this product is to manufacture [[MOX Fuel Rod|MOX Fuel Rods]], requiring 20 units of '''Plutonium Oxide Pellets''' along with 1 [[Zirconium Rod]] and 10 units of [[Yellowcake]]. This is proven to be the vital bridge into making one of the most complex, yet powerful type of rod for the [[Nuclear Power Plant]] to be used on.
== Recipes == {{Production|input1=mixed-fissile-oxides|input2=hydrochloric-acid|input3=sodium-hydroxide-solution|input4=argon|Input1Amount=0.5|Input2Amount=0.5|Input3Amount=0.5|Input4Amount=30|time=1|Mamyflux=500KMF|machine=Chemical Plant|output1=residue|output2=reprocessed-uranium|output3=plutonium-oxide-pellets|Output1Amount=3|Output2Amount=0.1|Output3Amount=0.05}}{{Production|input1=zirconium-rod|input2=plutonium-oxide-pellets|input3=yellowcake|output1=mox-fuel-rod|Output1Amount=1|time=5|Mamyflux=1MMF|machine=Precision Assembler|Input1Amount=1|Input2Amount=20|Input3Amount=10}}{{Items Navbox}}

{{Item|itemImage=Icon-nitrogen.png|research=Air Separation Unit|sellValue={{Money|0.15}}|resValue={{RP|0x }}}}
==Information==
'''Nitrogen''' is a chemical element that was introduced to the game on {{Update|1.0}}. It is produced from vaporizing [[Liquid Nitrogen]] via the [[Vaporizer]], changing the state of matter from liquid to gas as each liter of [[Liquid Nitrogen]] is equivalent to 30 liters of Nitrogen gas.

== Usage ==
'''Nitrogen''' is generally used for [[Ammonia]] and [[Mixed Fissile Nitrates|Mixed Fissile Nitrate]] productions via the [[Chemical Plant]] and [[Ore Enrichment Facility]], respectively. It becomes a highly vital resource when reprocessing [[Spent Fuel]] from [[Standard Fuel Rod|Standard Fuel Rods]] and [[Low Enrichment Fuel Rod|Low Enrichment Fuel Rods]], allowing the production of [[MOX Fuel Rod|MOX Fuel Rods]] once the latter has been processed thoroughly.

