{{Stub}}{{Item|itemImage=Icon-hydrofluoric-acid.png|sellValue={{Money|600}}|resValue={{RP|13x }}|research=Chemical Reactor, Advanced Chemical Plant}}
== Information == '''Hydrofluoric Acid''' is a type of acid that was introduced to the game on {{Update|1.0}}. This acid is obtained either from the [[Chemical Reactor]] or [[Chemical Plant]], using [[Sulfuric Acid]] and [[Deep Earth Fragment|Deep Earth Fragments]] as the main ingredients in order to produce the latter.
This acid plays a vital role whenever a player plans to use the [[Nuclear Power Plant]], as this is the first source where UF6 Gases can be manufactured, which are then purified via the [[Gas Centrifuge]].
== Usage == When '''Hydrofluoric Acid''' is mixed with [[Yellowcake]] or [[Reprocessed Uranium]] using the [[Chemical Plant]], it is able to produce [[Unenriched UF6 Gas]] and [[Slightly Enriched UF6 Gas]], respectively. Likewise, this is the only use for the said acid and can play a vital role whilst progressing through the game.
